F00:0582       ;----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
F00:0583       RM_init:
F00:0584       ; ne fait que verifier la version de Risc OS...
F00:0585       	str		lr,save_lr
               S01:00008294:  20 E0 8F E5
F00:0586       ; get OS version
F00:0587       	MOV     R0,#129
               S01:00008298:  81 00 A0 E3
F00:0588       	MOV     R1,#0
               S01:0000829C:  00 10 A0 E3
F00:0589       	MOV     R2,#0xFF
               S01:000082A0:  FF 20 A0 E3
F00:0590       	SWI     OS_Byte
               S01:000082A4:  06 00 00 EF
F00:0591       
F00:0592       	STRB    R1,os_version
               S01:000082A8:  0C 15 CF E5
F00:0593       
F00:0594       ; Risc os 3.5 ? => sortie
F00:0595       	CMP     R1,#0xA5
               S01:000082AC:  A5 00 51 E3
F00:0596       	beq		exit
               S01:000082B0:  C6 FF FF 0A
F00:0597       	
F00:0598       	ldr		lr,save_lr
               S01:000082B4:  00 E0 9F E5
F00:0599       	mov		pc,lr
               S01:000082B8:  0E F0 A0 E1
F00:0600       save_lr:		.long		0
               S01:000082BC:  00 00 00 00
F00:0601       
F00:0602       ; SH decoded IRQ and FIQ masks
F00:0603       ;
F00:0604       ; to load/set/store IRQ and FIQ masks use:
F00:0605       ;
F00:0606       ; Rx=mask
F00:0607       ; Ry=&3200000 (IOC base)
F00:0608       ;
F00:0609       ;
F00:0610       ; LDRB Rx,[Ry,#&18+0]      ;load irqa mask (+0)
F00:0611       ; STRB Rx,oldirqa          ;store original mask
F00:0612       ; MOV  Rx,#%00100000       ;only allow timer 0 interrupt
F00:0613       ; STRB Rx,[Ry,#&18+2]      ;(note +2 on storing)
F00:0614       ;
F00:0615       ; LDRB Rx,[Ry,#&28+0]      ;load irqb mask (+0)
F00:0616       ; STRB Rx,oldirqb          ;store original mask
F00:0617       ; MOV  Rx,#%00000010       ;only allow sound interrupt
F00:0618       ; STRB Rx,[Ry,#&28+2]      ;(note +2 on storing)
F00:0619       ;
F00:0620       ;
F00:0621       
F00:0622       ;irqa mask = IOC (&3200000) + &18
F00:0623       ;
F00:0624       ;bit 0   - il6 0 printer busy / printer irq
F00:0625       ;    1   - il7 0 serial port ringing / low battery
F00:0626       ;    2   - if  0 printer ack / floppy index
F00:0627       ;    3s  - ir  1 vsync
F00:0628       ;    4   - por 0 power on
F00:0629       ;    5c  - tm0 0 timer 0
F00:0630       ;    6   - tm1 1 timer 1
F00:0631       ;    7   - 1   0 n/c      (fiq downgrade?)
F00:0632       ;
F00:0633       ;irqb mask = IOC (&3200000) + &28
F00:0634       ;
F00:0635       ;bit 0   - il0 0 expansion card fiq downgrade
F00:0636       ;    1   - il1 0 sound system buffer change
F00:0637       ;    2   - il2 0 serial port controller
F00:0638       ;    3   - il3 0 hdd controller / ide controller
F00:0639       ;    4   - il4 0 floppy changed / floppy interrupt
F00:0640       ;    5   - il5 0 expansion card interrupt
F00:0641       ;    6   - stx 1 keyboard transmit empty
F00:0642       ;    7cs - str 1 keyboard recieve full
F00:0643       ;
F00:0644       ; c = cmdline critical
F00:0645       ; s = desktop critical
F00:0646       ;
F00:0647       ;fiq mask (none are critical) = IOC (&3200000) + &38
F00:0648       ;
F00:0649       ;bit 0  - fh0 0 floppy data request / floppy dma
F00:0650       ;    1  - fh1 0 fdc interrupt / fh1 pin on ioc
F00:0651       ;    2  - fl  0 econet interrupt
F00:0652       ;    3  - c3  0 c3 on ioc
F00:0653       ;    4  - c4  0 c4 on ioc / serial interrupt (also IRQB bit2)
F00:0654       ;    5  - c5  0 c5 on ioc
F00:0655       ;    6  - il0 0 expansion card interrupt
F00:0656       ;    7  - 1   0 force fiq (always 1)
F00:0657       ;
F00:0658       ;cr
F00:0659       ;
F00:0660       ;bit 0 - c0 IIC data
F00:0661       ;    1 - c1 IIC clock
F00:0662       ;    2 - c2 floppy ready / density
F00:0663       ;    3 - c3 reset enable / unique id
F00:0664       ;    4 - c4 aux i/o connector / serial fiq
F00:0665       ;    5 - c5 speaker
F00:0666       ;    6 - if printer ack or floppy index
F00:0667       ;    7 - ir vsync
F00:0668       ;	
F00:0669       ;----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
F00:0670       RM_start:
F00:0671       	str		lr,save_lr
               S01:000082C0:  0C E0 0F E5
F00:0672       ; appel XOS car si appel OS_SWI si erreur, ça sort directement
F00:0673       	MOV		R0,#0x0C           ;claim FIQ
               S01:000082C4:  0C 00 A0 E3
F00:0674       	SWI		XOS_ServiceCall
               S01:000082C8:  30 00 02 EF
F00:0675       	bvs		exit
               S01:000082CC:  BF FF FF 6A
F00:0676       
F00:0677       
F00:0678       ; we own FIQs
F00:0679       
F00:0680       
F00:0681       	TEQP	PC,#0xC000001					; bit 27 & 26 = 1, bit 0=1 : IRQ Disable+FIRQ Disable+FIRQ mode ( pour récupérer et sauvegarde
               S01:000082D0:  43 F3 3F E3
F00:0682       ;	TEQP	PC,#0b11<<26 OR 0b01			;disable IRQs and FIQs, change to FIQ mode
F00:0683       	MOV		R0,R0
               S01:000082D4:  00 00 A0 E1
F00:0684       
F00:0685       	ADR       R0,fiqoriginal				; sauvegarde de R8-R14
               S01:000082D8:  01 0B 8F E2 E0 00 80 E2
F00:0686       	STMIA     R0,{R8-R14}
               S01:000082E0:  00 7F 80 E8
F00:0687       
F00:0688       	MOV       R1,#0x3200000
               S01:000082E4:  32 16 A0 E3
F00:0689       	LDRB      R0,[R1,#0x18]					; lecture et sauvegarde mask IRQ A
               S01:000082E8:  18 00 D1 E5
F00:0690       	STR       R0,oldIRQa
               S01:000082EC:  E8 04 8F E5
F00:0691       	LDRB      R0,[R1,#0x28]					; lecture et sauvegarde mask IRQ B
               S01:000082F0:  28 00 D1 E5
F00:0692       	STR       R0,oldIRQb
               S01:000082F4:  E4 04 8F E5
F00:0693       
F00:0694       ; When installing, we will start on the next VSync, so set IRQ for VSync only
F00:0695       ; and set T1 to contain 'vsyncvalue', so everything in place for VSync int...
F00:0696       
F00:0697       	MOV       R0,#0b00001000
               S01:000082F8:  08 00 A0 E3
F00:0698       	STRB      R0,[R1,#0x18+2]    ;set IRQA mask to %00001000 = VSync only : bit 3 sur mask IRQ A = vsync
               S01:000082FC:  1A 00 C1 E5
F00:0699       	MOV       R0,#0
               S01:00008300:  00 00 A0 E3
F00:0700       	STRB      R0,[R1,#0x28+2]    ;set IRQB mask to 0					:	IRQ B mask à 0 = disabled
               S01:00008304:  2A 00 C1 E5
F00:0701       	STRB      R0,[R1,#0x38+2]    ;set FIQ mask to 0 (disable FIQs)		:	FIRQ  mask à 0 = disabled
               S01:00008308:  3A 00 C1 E5
F00:0702       
F00:0703       ; Timer 1 / IRQ A
F00:0704       	MOV       R0,#0xFF           ;*v0.14* set max T1 - ensure T1 doesn't trigger before first VSync!
               S01:0000830C:  FF 00 A0 E3
F00:0705       	STRB      R0,[R1,#0x50+2]    ;T1 low byte, +2 for write			: verrou / compteur = 0xFFFF
               S01:00008310:  52 00 C1 E5
F00:0706       	STRB      R0,[R1,#0x54+2]    ;T1 high byte, +2 for write
               S01:00008314:  56 00 C1 E5
F00:0707       	STRB      R1,[R1,#0x58+2]    ;T1_go = reset T1					: remet le compteur a la valeur latch ( verrou)
               S01:00008318:  5A 10 C1 E5
F00:0708       
F00:0709       ; on prépare le compteur du Timer 1 qui tournera entre le Vsync et la 1ere ligne de hsync
F00:0710       	MOV       R0,#vsyncreturn_low_ligne199			;or ldr r8,vsyncval  - will reload with this on VSync...			
               S01:0000831C:  A5 00 A0 E3
F00:0711       	STRB      R0,[R1,#0x50+2]    				;T1 low byte, +2 for write									: verrou / compteur 
               S01:00008320:  52 00 C1 E5
F00:0712       	MOV       R0,#vsyncreturn_high_ligne199			;or mov r8,r8,lsr#8
               S01:00008324:  7E 00 A0 E3
F00:0713       	STRB      R0,[R1,#0x54+2]   					;T1 high byte, +2 for write								: verrou / compteur 
               S01:00008328:  56 00 C1 E5
F00:0714       
F00:0715       
F00:0716       ; poke our IRQ/FIQ code into &1C-&FC : copie des routines IRQ/FIRQ dans la mémoire basse en 0x18
F00:0717       	MOV       R0,#0
               S01:0000832C:  00 00 A0 E3
F00:0718       	LDR       R1,[R0,#0x18]      ;load current IRQ vector
               S01:00008330:  18 10 90 E5
F00:0719       	STR       R1,oldIRQbranch
               S01:00008334:  AC 14 8F E5
F00:0720       
F00:0721       	BIC       R1,R1,#0xFF000000
               S01:00008338:  FF 14 C1 E3

F00:1546       ;--------------------------------------------------------------------
F00:1547       ;    Transformation
F00:1548       ;--------------------------------------------------------------------
F00:1549       
F00:1550       ;- dans la boucle d'initialisation des animations :
F00:1551       ;
F00:1552       ;	- calculer deltaX/nb etapes, delta Y / nb etapes, delta Z/nb etapes
F00:1553       ;	- multiplier chaque valeur par 2^15
F00:1554       ;	- stocker dans table_increments_pas_transformations : X source ,increment X, Y source, increment Y, Z source, incremen
F00:1555       ;			pointeur_table_increments_pas_transformations
F00:1556       ; fonction : preparation_transformation:
F00:1557       ;
F00:1558       ;
F00:1559       ;- dans la boucle de calcul des rotations/projections
F00:1560       ;	- remplir pointeur_buffer_coordonnees_objet_transformees:
F00:1561       ;		- avec calcul de table_increments_pas_transformations  : X + inc X, Y+inc Y , Z+inc Z, 
F00:1562       ;		- stocker le resultat dans table_increments_pas_transformations +0 +8 + 16
F00:1563       ;		- stocker le resultat / 2^15 dans pointeur_buffer_coordonnees_objet_transformees
F00:1564       
F00:1565       
F00:1566       preparation_transformation:
F00:1567       
F00:1568       
F00:1569       
F00:1570       		ldr		R12,pointeur_table_increments_pas_transformations						; destination pour les X Y Z et increments
               S01:00008D90:  7C C8 9F E5
F00:1571       		ldr		R11,pointeur_coordonnees_objet_source_transformation					; points de l'objet source : X Y Z n°sprite
               S01:00008D94:  50 B8 9F E5
F00:1572       		ldr		R10,pointeur_coordonnees_objet_destination_transformation				; coordonnees objet destination : X Y Z n°sprite
               S01:00008D98:  50 A8 9F E5
F00:1573       		
F00:1574       		ldr		R9,nb_etapes_transformation
               S01:00008D9C:  58 98 9F E5
F00:1575       		
F00:1576       		ldr		R0,nb_points_objet_en_cours
               S01:00008DA0:  10 08 9F E5
F00:1577       		
F00:1578       boucle_preparation_transformation:
F00:1579       		
F00:1580       		mov		R7,#3
               S01:00008DA4:  03 70 A0 E3
F00:1581       		
F00:1582       boucle_preparation_transformation_1_valeur:
F00:1583       
F00:1584       		ldr		R1,[R11],#4					; on recupere X point objet source
               S01:00008DA8:  04 10 9B E4
F00:1585       		ldr		R2,[R10],#4					; on recupere X point objet destination
               S01:00008DAC:  04 20 9A E4
F00:1586       		
F00:1587       		subs	R3,R2,R1					; Delta X = X destination - X source
               S01:00008DB0:  01 30 52 E0
F00:1588       
F00:1589       ; calcul du pas : il faut diviser R3 par R9
F00:1590       ; en tenant compte de R3 négatif ?
F00:1591       
F00:1592       ; si r3 négatif :
F00:1593        	mov R4,#0
               S01:00008DB4:  00 40 A0 E3
F00:1594       	
F00:1595       
F00:1596       	cmp r3,#0
               S01:00008DB8:  00 00 53 E3
F00:1597       	bpl .deltaX_positif
               S01:00008DBC:  01 00 00 5A
F00:1598       ; r11 négatif
F00:1599       
F00:1600       	rsb r3,r3,#0
               S01:00008DC0:  00 30 63 E2
F00:1601       	mov r4,#1		; R5 = 1 si X negatif
               S01:00008DC4:  01 40 A0 E3
F00:1602       
F00:1603       .deltaX_positif:
F00:1604       	mov		R3,R3,asl #15				; * 2^15
               S01:00008DC8:  83 37 A0 E1
F00:1605       
F00:1606       ; R5 = ( R3 / R9 )
F00:1607       ; registres dispos	:  R5 R6 R7 R8 R13 R14
F00:1608       
F00:1609       	MOV      R5,#0     ;clear R5 to accumulate result
               S01:00008DCC:  00 50 A0 E3
F00:1610       	MOV      R6,#1     ;set bit 0 in R6, which will be
               S01:00008DD0:  01 60 A0 E3
F00:1611       					   ;shifted left then right
F00:1612       .startdivX_transformation1:
F00:1613       	CMP      R9,R3
               S01:00008DD4:  03 00 59 E1
F00:1614       	MOVLS    R9,R9,LSL#1
               S01:00008DD8:  89 90 A0 91
F00:1615       	MOVLS    R6,R6,LSL#1
               S01:00008DDC:  86 60 A0 91
F00:1616       	BLS      .startdivX_transformation1
               S01:00008DE0:  FB FF FF 9A
F00:1617       
F00:1618       .nextdivX_transformation1:
F00:1619       	CMP       R3,R9
               S01:00008DE4:  09 00 53 E1
F00:1620       	SUBCS     R3,R3,R9
               S01:00008DE8:  09 30 43 20
F00:1621       	ADDCS     R5,R5,R6
               S01:00008DEC:  06 50 85 20
F00:1622       	MOVS      R6,R6,LSR#1
               S01:00008DF0:  A6 60 B0 E1
F00:1623       	MOVCC     R9,R9,LSR#1
               S01:00008DF4:  A9 90 A0 31
F00:1624       	BCC			.nextdivX_transformation1
               S01:00008DF8:  F9 FF FF 3A
F00:1625       
F00:1626       	cmp		R4,#0			; R3 était négatif ?
               S01:00008DFC:  00 00 54 E3
F00:1627       	beq		.X_transformation_negatif
               S01:00008E00:  00 00 00 0A
F00:1628       	rsb		r5,r5,#0		; alors résultat négatif
               S01:00008E04:  00 50 65 E2
F00:1629       	
F00:1630       .X_transformation_negatif:
F00:1631       
F00:1632       ; R5 = R3/R9
F00:1633       
F00:1634       	mov		R1,R1,asl #15	; X * 2^15
               S01:00008E08:  81 17 A0 E1
F00:1635       	
F00:1636       	str		R1,[R12],#4		; on stocke X * 2^15
               S01:00008E0C:  04 10 8C E4
F00:1637       	str		R5,[R12],#4		; increment X * 2^15
               S01:00008E10:  04 50 8C E4
F00:1638       	
F00:1639       	subs	R7,R7,#1
               S01:00008E14:  01 70 57 E2
F00:1640       	bgt		boucle_preparation_transformation_1_valeur
               S01:00008E18:  E2 FF FF CA
F00:1641       	
F00:1642       	ldr		R7,[R11],#4			; n° sprite source
               S01:00008E1C:  04 70 9B E4
F00:1643       	add		R10,R10,#4			; on saute le n° sprite objet destination
               S01:00008E20:  04 A0 8A E2
F00:1644       	str		R7,[R12],#4			; n° sprite table increment
               S01:00008E24:  04 70 8C E4
F00:1645       		
F00:1646       	subs	R0,R0,#1
               S01:00008E28:  01 00 50 E2
F00:1647       	bgt		boucle_preparation_transformation
               S01:00008E2C:  DC FF FF CA
F00:1648       ; sortie
F00:1649       	mov pc, r14
               S01:00008E30:  0E F0 A0 E1
F00:1650       
F00:1651       
F00:1652       ;--------------	
F00:1653       ;	calcul progressif des X Y Z transformation
F00:1654       ;	source : pointeur_table_increments_pas_transformations : X source ,increment X, Y source, increment Y, Z source, incre
F00:1655       ;	dest : pointeur_buffer_coordonnees_objet_transformees
F00:1656

F00:1659

               S01:00008E34:  BC C7 9F E5

F00:1667       		mov		R7,#3
               S01:00008E40:  03 70 A0 E3

F00:1670       		ldr		R1,[R11]					; X * 2^15
               S01:00008E44:  00 10 9B E5

               S01:00008E48:  04 20 9B E5

F00:2746       calc3D:
F00:2747       ; input : 
F00:2748       ;	- pointeur_points_objet_en_cours = pointeur vers les points 3D X,Y,Z
F00:2749       ;	- nb_points_objet_en_cours = nombre de points à calculer

F00:2751

               S01:00009720:  04 E3 8F E5

F00:2754       	; calcul de la matrice de transformation

F00:2756       	ldr r11,pointeur_SINCOS
               S01:00009724:  34 B3 9F E5
F00:2757       	
F00:2758       	
F00:2759       	ldr r1,angleX

               S01:0000972C:  81 11 8B E0

F00:2774       	RSB r6,r6,#0
               S01:0000974C:  00 60 66 E2

F00:2778

F00:2780

               S01:00009750:  95 07 1E E0

F00:3234           MOV     R2,#0               ;// R2 = Current Element Number
               S01:00009A78:  00 20 A0 E3
F00:3235           MOV     R6,#0               ;// R6 = Number of swaps
               S01:00009A7C:  00 60 A0 E3
F00:3236       bsort_loop:                     ;// Start loop
F00:3237           ADD     R3,R2,#1            ;// R3 = Next Element Number
               S01:00009A80:  01 30 82 E2
F00:3238           CMP     R3,R1               ;// Check for the end of the array
               S01:00009A84:  01 00 53 E1
F00:3239           BGE     bsort_check         ;// When we reach the end, check for changes
               S01:00009A88:  13 00 00 AA
F00:3240           LDR     R4,[R0,R2,LSL #4]   ;// R4 = Current Element Value
               S01:00009A8C:  02 42 90 E7
F00:3241           LDR     R5,[R0,R3,LSL #4]   ;// R5 = Next Element Value
               S01:00009A90:  03 52 90 E7
F00:3242           CMP     R5,R4               ;// Compare element values
               S01:00009A94:  04 00 55 E1
F00:3243

               S01:00009A98:  02 52 80 C7
F00:3246           STRGT   R4,[R0,R3,LSL #4]   ;// If R4 > R5, Store next value at current
               S01:00009A9C:  03 42 80 C7

F00:3265           MOV     R2,R3               ;// Advance to the next element
               S01:00009AD4:  03 20 A0 E1
F00:3266           B       bsort_loop          ;// End loop
               S01:00009AD8:  E8 FF FF EA
F00:3267       bsort_check:                    ;// Check for changes
F00:3268           CMP     R6,#0               ;// Were there changes this iteration?
               S01:00009ADC:  00 00 56 E3
F00:3269           SUBGT   R1,R1,#1            ;// Optimization: skip last value in next loop
               S01:00009AE0:  01 10 41 C2
F00:3270           BGT     bsort_next          ;// If there were changes, do it again
               S01:00009AE4:  E3 FF FF CA
F00:3271       bsort_done: 
F00:3272       
F00:3273       	mov		pc,lr
               S01:00009AE8:  0E F0 A0 E1
F00:3274       
F00:3275       ;-------------------------------------------
F00:3276       copie_dans_buffer_calcul_final:
F00:3277       
F00:3278       ; encodage :
F00:3279       ; 9 bits pour X
F00:3280       ; 9 bits pour Y
F00:3281       ; 4 bits pour n° sprite
F00:3282       ; = 22 bits , reste 10 bits
F00:3283       
F00:3284       ; X << 13
F00:3285       ; Y << 4
F00:3286       ; X peut etre negatif
F00:3287       ; Y ne peut pas etre negatif
F00:3288       ; n° ne peut pas etre negatif
F00:3289       
F00:3290       
F00:3291       
F00:3292       	ldr		R0,nb_points_objet_en_cours_au_total
               S01:00009AEC:  38 05 1F E5
F00:3293       	
F00:3294       	ldr		R11,pointeur_coordonnees_projetees			; source
               S01:00009AF0:  4C B5 1F E5
F00:3295       	ldr		R12,pointeur_actuel_buffer_en_cours_de_calcul		; destination
               S01:00009AF4:  6C C5 1F E5
F00:3296       	
F00:3297       	ldr		r13,pointeur_table416
               S01:00009AF8:  38 D4 9F E5
F00:3298       	
F00:3299       .boucle_copie_avec_reduction:
F00:3300       
F00:3301       
F00:3302       	ldmia	R11!,{R1-R4}
               S01:00009AFC:  1E 00 BB E8
F00:3303       
F00:3304       	
F00:3305       ;	ldr		R1,[R11],#4				; X projeté écran
F00:3306       ;	ldr		R2,[R11],#4				; Y projeté écran
F00:3307       ;	add		R11,R11,#4				; on saute le Z
F00:3308       ;	ldr		R4,[R11],#4				; n° sprite
F00:3309       
F00:3310       ; on calcule le position ecran
F00:3311       	ldr		R2,[r13,R2,asl #2]		; R2=Y * 416
               S01:00009B00:  02 21 9D E7
F00:3312       	adds	R2,R2,R1				; R1 = position mémoire écran : X + 416 * Y
               S01:00009B04:  01 20 92 E0
F00:3313       ; valeur maxi : 107 328 : 18 bits
F00:3314       ; il faut garder le bas du X pour choisir le bon décalage de  sprite
F00:3315       ;	mov		R2,R2,asl #2			; 2 bits pour position X 
F00:3316       
F00:3317       ;	and		R1,R1,#0b11				; on garde la position X sur 4
F00:3318       ;	adds	R2,R2,R1				; on ajoute à la position mémoire
F00:3319       	mov		R2,R2,asl #4			; + 4 bits pour le n° sprite 
               S01:00009B08:  02 22 A0 E1
F00:3320       	adds	R2,R2,R4				; + n° sprite		
               S01:00009B0C:  04 20 92 E0
F00:3321       	
F00:3322       	str		R2,[R12],#4
               S01:00009B10:  04 20 8C E4
F00:3323       ; décodage
F00:3324       ; R1 = Y*416 +x << 4 + n° sprite
F00:3325       ; cible : R4=position, R5 = X n° décalage, R6 = n° sprite
F00:3326       ;	and		R6,R2,#0b1111
F00:3327       ;	mov		R2,R2,asr #4
F00:3328       ;	and		R5,R2,#0b11
F00:3329       ;	mov		R4,R2,asr #2
F00:3330       	
F00:3331       	
F00:3332       	
F00:3333       	subs	R0,R0,#1
               S01:00009B14:  01 00 50 E2
F00:3334       	bgt		.boucle_copie_avec_reduction
               S01:00009B18:  F7 FF FF CA
F00:3335       	
F00:3336       
F00:3337       	mov		pc,lr
               S01:00009B1C:  0E F0 A0 E1
F00:3338       
F00:3339       pointeur_pile_quick_sort:		.long	pile_quick_sort
               S01:00009B20:  00 4D 02 00
F00:3340       
F00:3341       ; ------------------------------------------------------------
F00:3342       ;
F00:3343       ; QUICK SORT
F00:3344       ;
F00:3345       ; ------------------------------------------------------------
F00:3346       
F00:3347       
F00:3348       quick_sort:
F00:3349       
F00:3350       
F00:3351       ; X Y Z n0 sprite=> 4 * 4 = 16 octets
F00:3352       	ldr		R10,pointeur_coordonnees_projetees			; R10 = X
               S01:00009B24:  80 A5 1F E5
F00:3353       	add		R11,R10,#4							; R11 = Y
               S01:00009B28:  04 B0 8A E2
F00:3354       	add		R12,R11,#4							; R12	= Z
               S01:00009B2C:  04 C0 8B E2
F00:3355       	;add		R13,R12,#4							; R13 = n° sprite
F00:3356       	
F00:3357       	ldr		R1,nb_points_objet_en_cours
               S01:00009B30:  80 15 1F E5
F00:3358       	
F00:3359       	ldr		R13,pointeur_pile_quick_sort
               S01:00009B34:  1C D0 1F E5
F00:3360       
F00:3361       qsort:
F00:3362       ; push de tous les registres
F00:3363       	stmdb	R13!,{R0-R12,LR}
               S01:00009B38:  FF 5F 2D E9
F00:3364       	
F00:3365       	MOV     R4,R12               ;// R4 = Array Location ( Z )
               S01:00009B3C:  0C 40 A0 E1
F00:3366       	MOV     R5,R1               ;// R5 - Array Size
               S01:00009B40:  01 50 A0 E1
F00:3367       	CMP     R5,#1               ;// Check for an array of size <= 1
               S01:00009B44:  01 00 55 E3
F00:3368           BLE     qsort_done          ;// If array size <= 1, return
               S01:00009B48:  66 00 00 DA
F00:3369       	
F00:3370       	CMP     R5,#2               ;// Check for an array of size == 2
               S01:00009B4C:  02 00 55 E3
F00:3371       	BEQ     qsort_check         ;// If array size == 2, check values
               S01:00009B50:  4F 00 00 0A
F00:3372       	
F00:3373       qsort_partition:
F00:3374       	mov		R2,R5,lsr #1		 ;// R2 = The middle element index , R1 / 2
               S01:00009B54:  A5 20 A0 E1
F00:3375       	LDR     R6,[R4]             ;// R6 = Beginning of array value
               S01:00009B58:  00 60 94 E5
F00:3376       	LDR     R7,[R4,R2,LSL #4]   ;// R7 = Middle of array value, *16 car X Y Z N°sprite = 16 octets
               S01:00009B5C:  02 72 94 E7
F00:3377       	SUB     R8,R5,#1             ;// R8 = Upper array bound index (len -1 1)
               S01:00009B60:  01 80 45 E2
F00:3378       	LDR     R8,[R4,R8,LSL #4]   ;// R8 = End of the array value , *16 car X Y Z N°sprite = 16 octets
               S01:00009B64:  08 82 94 E7
F00:3379       	
F00:3380       	CMP     R6,R7                ;// Sort the values
               S01:00009B68:  07 00 56 E1
F00:3381       	MOVGT   R9,R6				 ;// echange R6 et R7
               S01:00009B6C:  06 90 A0 C1
F00:3382           MOVGT   R6,R7
               S01:00009B70:  07 60 A0 C1
F00:3383           MOVGT   R7,R9
               S01:00009B74:  09 70 A0 C1
F00:3384       	
F00:3385       	CMP     R7,R8
               S01:00009B78:  08 00 57 E1
F00:3386           MOVGT   R9,R7				 ;// echange R7 et R8
               S01:00009B7C:  07 90 A0 C1
F00:3387           MOVGT   R7,R8
               S01:00009B80:  08 70 A0 C1
F00:3388           MOVGT   R8,R9
               S01:00009B84:  09 80 A0 C1
F00:3389       	
F00:3390       	CMP     R6,R7
               S01:00009B88:  07 00 56 E1
F00:3391           MOVGT   R9,R6				 ;// echange R6 et R7 
               S01:00009B8C:  06 90 A0 C1
F00:3392           MOVGT   R6,R7
               S01:00009B90:  07 60 A0 C1
F00:3393           MOVGT   R7,R9
               S01:00009B94:  09 70 A0 C1
F00:3394       	
F00:3395       	MOV     R6,R7                ;// R6 = Pivot
               S01:00009B98:  07 60 A0 E1
F00:3396       	MOV     R7,#0                ;// R7 = Lower array bounds index
               S01:00009B9C:  00 70 A0 E3
F00:3397       	SUB     R8,R5,#1             ;// R8 = Upper array bounds index (len - 1)
               S01:00009BA0:  01 80 45 E2
F00:3398       
F00:3399       qsort_loop:
F00:3400       	LDR     R0,[R4,R7,LSL #4]   ;// R0 = Lower value, Z, *16 car X Y Z N°sprite = 16 octets
               S01:00009BA4:  07 02 94 E7
F00:3401       	LDR     R1,[R4,R8,LSL #4]   ;// R1 = Upper value , Z
               S01:00009BA8:  08 12 94 E7
F00:3402       	CMP     R0,R6               ;// Compare lower value to pivot
               S01:00009BAC:  06 00 50 E1
F00:3403       	BEQ     qsort_loop_u        ;// If == pivot, do nothing
               S01:00009BB0:  16 00 00 0A
F00:3404       	ADDLT   R7,R7,#1            ;// If < pivot, increment lower index
               S01:00009BB4:  01 70 87 B2
F00:3405       	STRGE   R0,[R4,R8,LSL #4]  ; // If > pivot, swap values
               S01:00009BB8:  08 02 84 A7
F00:3406       	STRGE   R1,[R4,R7,LSL #4]
               S01:00009BBC:  07 12 84 A7
F00:3407       ; X
F00:3408       	sub		R10,R4,#8			; position Z - 8 = X
               S01:00009BC0:  08 A0 44 E2
F00:3409       	LDRGE	R0,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; X1
               S01:00009BC4:  07 02 9A A7
F00:3410       	LDRGE	R1,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; X2
               S01:00009BC8:  08 12 9A A7
F00:3411       	STRGE   R0,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; X1
               S01:00009BCC:  08 02 8A A7
F00:3412       	STRGE   R1,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; X2
               S01:00009BD0:  07 12 8A A7
F00:3413       ; Y
F00:3414       	add		R10,R10,#4			; passe à position Y
               S01:00009BD4:  04 A0 8A E2
F00:3415       	LDRGE	R0,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; Y1
               S01:00009BD8:  07 02 9A A7
F00:3416       	LDRGE	R1,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; Y2
               S01:00009BDC:  08 12 9A A7
F00:3417       	STRGE   R0,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; Y1
               S01:00009BE0:  08 02 8A A7
F00:3418       	STRGE   R1,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; Y2
               S01:00009BE4:  07 12 8A A7
F00:3419       ; n° sprite
F00:3420       	add		R10,R10,#8			; passe à position n°sprite
               S01:00009BE8:  08 A0 8A E2
F00:3421       	LDRGE	R0,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; n° 1
               S01:00009BEC:  07 02 9A A7
F00:3422       	LDRGE	R1,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; n°2
               S01:00009BF0:  08 12 9A A7
F00:3423       	STRGE   R0,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; n°1
               S01:00009BF4:  08 02 8A A7
F00:3424       	STRGE   R1,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; n°2
               S01:00009BF8:  07 12 8A A7
F00:3425       
F00:3426       	SUBGE   R8,R8,#1            ; // if > pivot, decrement upper index
               S01:00009BFC:  01 80 48 A2
F00:3427       	CMP     R7,R8               ; // if indexes are the same, recurse
               S01:00009C00:  08 00 57 E1
F00:3428       	BEQ     qsort_recurse
               S01:00009C04:  18 00 00 0A
F00:3429       	LDR     R0,[R4,R7,LSL #4]  ; // R0 = Lower value
               S01:00009C08:  07 02 94 E7
F00:3430       	LDR     R1,[R4,R8,LSL #4]  ; // R1 = Upper value
               S01:00009C0C:  08 12 94 E7
F00:3431       
F00:3432       qsort_loop_u:
F00:3433       	CMP     R1,R6               ; // Compare upper value to pivot
               S01:00009C10:  06 00 51 E1
F00:3434       	SUBGT   R8,R8,#1            ; // if > pivot, decrement upper index
               S01:00009C14:  01 80 48 C2
F00:3435       	STRLE   R0,[R4,R8,LSL #4]  ; // If < pivot, swap values
               S01:00009C18:  08 02 84 D7
F00:3436       	STRLE   R1,[R4,R7,LSL #4]
               S01:00009C1C:  07 12 84 D7
F00:3437       
F00:3438       ; X
F00:3439       	sub		R10,R4,#8			; position Z - 8 = X
               S01:00009C20:  08 A0 44 E2
F00:3440       	LDRLE	R0,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; X1
               S01:00009C24:  07 02 9A D7
F00:3441       	LDRLE	R1,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; X2
               S01:00009C28:  08 12 9A D7
F00:3442       	STRLE   R0,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; X1
               S01:00009C2C:  08 02 8A D7
F00:3443       	STRLE   R1,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; X2
               S01:00009C30:  07 12 8A D7
F00:3444       ; Y
F00:3445       	add		R10,R10,#4			; passe à position Y
               S01:00009C34:  04 A0 8A E2
F00:3446       	LDRLE	R0,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; Y1
               S01:00009C38:  07 02 9A D7
F00:3447       	LDRLE	R1,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; Y2
               S01:00009C3C:  08 12 9A D7
F00:3448       	STRLE   R0,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; Y1
               S01:00009C40:  08 02 8A D7
F00:3449       	STRLE   R1,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; Y2
               S01:00009C44:  07 12 8A D7
F00:3450       ; n° sprite
F00:3451       	add		R10,R10,#8			; passe à position n°sprite
               S01:00009C48:  08 A0 8A E2
F00:3452       	LDRLE	R0,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; n° 1
               S01:00009C4C:  07 02 9A D7
F00:3453       	LDRLE	R1,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; n°2
               S01:00009C50:  08 12 9A D7
F00:3454       	STRLE   R0,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; n°1
               S01:00009C54:  08 02 8A D7
F00:3455       	STRLE   R1,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; n°2	
               S01:00009C58:  07 12 8A D7
F00:3456       	
F00:3457       	
F00:3458       	ADDLE   R7,R7,#1			; // if < pivot, increment lower index
               S01:00009C5C:  01 70 87 D2
F00:3459       	CMP     R7,R8               ; // if indexes are the same, recurse
               S01:00009C60:  08 00 57 E1
F00:3460       	BEQ     qsort_recurse
               S01:00009C64:  00 00 00 0A
F00:3461       	B       qsort_loop          ; // Continue loop
               S01:00009C68:  CD FF FF EA
F00:3462       	
F00:3463       qsort_recurse:
F00:3464       	MOV     R12,R4              ; // R0 = Location of the first bucket
               S01:00009C6C:  04 C0 A0 E1
F00:3465       	MOV     R1,R7               ; // R1 = Length of the first bucket
               S01:00009C70:  07 10 A0 E1
F00:3466       	BL      qsort               ; // Sort first bucket
               S01:00009C74:  AF FF FF EB
F00:3467       	ADD     R8,R8,#1            ; // R8 = 1 index past final index
               S01:00009C78:  01 80 88 E2
F00:3468       	CMP     R8,R5               ; // Compare final index to original length
               S01:00009C7C:  05 00 58 E1
F00:3469       	BGE     qsort_done          ; // If equal, return
               S01:00009C80:  18 00 00 AA
F00:3470       	ADD     R12,R4,R8,LSL #4    ; // R0 = Location of the second bucket , *16 car X Y Z N°sprite = 16 octets
               S01:00009C84:  08 C2 84 E0
F00:3471       	SUB     R1,R5,R8            ; // R1 = Length of the second bucket
               S01:00009C88:  08 10 45 E0
F00:3472       	BL      qsort               ; // Sort second bucket
               S01:00009C8C:  A9 FF FF EB
F00:3473       	B       qsort_done          ; // return
               S01:00009C90:  14 00 00 EA
F00:3474       	
F00:3475       qsort_check:
F00:3476       	LDR     R0,[R4]             ; // Load first value into R0
               S01:00009C94:  00 00 94 E5
F00:3477       	LDR     R1,[R4,#16]          ; // Load second value into R1
               S01:00009C98:  10 10 94 E5
F00:3478       	CMP     R0,R1               ; // Compare R0 and R1
               S01:00009C9C:  01 00 50 E1
F00:3479       	BLE     qsort_done          ; // If R1 <= R0, then we are done
               S01:00009CA0:  10 00 00 DA
F00:3480       	
F00:3481       	STR     R1,[R4]             ; // Otherwise, swap values
               S01:00009CA4:  00 10 84 E5
F00:3482       	STR     R0,[R4,#16]          ; //  *16 car X Y Z N°sprite = 16 octets
               S01:00009CA8:  10 00 84 E5
F00:3483       ; X
F00:3484       	sub		R10,R4,#8			; position Z - 8 = X
               S01:00009CAC:  08 A0 44 E2
F00:3485       	LDR		R0,[R10]			; X1
               S01:00009CB0:  00 00 9A E5
F00:3486       	LDR		R1,[R10,#16]		; X2
               S01:00009CB4:  10 10 9A E5
F00:3487       	STR	    R1,[R10]	; X1
               S01:00009CB8:  00 10 8A E5
F00:3488       	STR	    R0,[R10, #16]	; X2
               S01:00009CBC:  10 00 8A E5
F00:3489       ; Y
F00:3490       	add		R10,R10,#4			; passe à position Y
               S01:00009CC0:  04 A0 8A E2
F00:3491       	LDR		R0,[R10]			; X1
               S01:00009CC4:  00 00 9A E5
F00:3492       	LDR		R1,[R10,#16]		; X2
               S01:00009CC8:  10 10 9A E5
F00:3493       	STR	    R1,[R10]	; X1
               S01:00009CCC:  00 10 8A E5
F00:3494       	STR	    R0,[R10, #16]	; X2
               S01:00009CD0:  10 00 8A E5
F00:3495       ; n° sprite
F00:3496       	add		R10,R10,#8			; passe à position n°sprite
               S01:00009CD4:  08 A0 8A E2
F00:3497       	LDR		R0,[R10]			; X1
               S01:00009CD8:  00 00 9A E5
F00:3498       	LDR		R1,[R10,#16]		; X2
               S01:00009CDC:  10 10 9A E5
F00:3499       	STR	    R1,[R10]	; X1
               S01:00009CE0:  00 10 8A E5
F00:3500       	STR	    R0,[R10, #16]	; X2
               S01:00009CE4:  10 00 8A E5
F00:3501       
F00:3502       
F00:3503       
F00:3504       qsort_done:
F00:3505       
F00:3506       ; pop de tous les registres
F00:3507       	ldmia	R13!,{R0-R12,PC}
               S01:00009CE8:  FF 9F BD E8
F00:3508       
F00:3509       ; ------------------------------------------------------------
F00:3510       ;
F00:3511       ; QUICK SORT 2eme version
F00:3512       ;
F00:3513       ; ------------------------------------------------------------
F00:3514       
F00:3515       
F00:3516       	
F00:3517       
F00:3518       quick_sort2:
F00:3519       ;  qsort:  @ Takes three parameters:
F00:3520       
F00:3521       ; R0 = pointeur vers le tableau de valeurs
F00:3522       ; R1 = 0
F00:3523       ; R2 = nb elements
F00:3524       
F00:3525       		ldr		sp,pointeur_pile_quick_sort
               S01:00009CEC:  D4 D1 1F E5
F00:3526       
F00:3527       		ldr		R0,pointeur_coordonnees_projetees
               S01:00009CF0:  4C 07 1F E5
F00:3528       
F00:3529       
F00:3530       		add		R0,R0,#8			; pointe sur Z
               S01:00009CF4:  08 00 80 E2
F00:3531       
F00:3532       		mov		R1,#0				; on commence à 0
               S01:00009CF8:  00 10 A0 E3
F00:3533       		ldr		R2,nb_points_objet_en_cours_au_total
               S01:00009CFC:  48 27 1F E5
F00:3534       
F00:3535       ; dispos : R8 R9 R10 R11 R12 
F00:3536       
F00:3537       qsort2_qsort:
F00:3538       ;        @   a:     Pointer to base of array a to be sorted (arrives in r0)
F00:3539       ;        @   left:  First of the range of indexes to sort (arrives in r1)
F00:3540       ;        @   right: One past last of range of indexes to sort (arrives in r2)
F00:3541       ;        @ This function destroys: r1, r2, r3, r5, r7
F00:3542       
F00:3543               stmfd   sp!, {r4, r6, lr}     ; @ Save r4 and r6 for caller
               S01:00009D00:  50 40 2D E9
F00:3544               mov     r6, r2                ; @ r6 <- right
               S01:00009D04:  02 60 A0 E1
F00:3545       
F00:3546       qsort2_qsort_tailcall_entry:
F00:3547               sub     r7, r6, r1            ; @ If right - left <= 1 (already sorted),
               S01:00009D08:  01 70 46 E0
F00:3548               cmp     r7, #1
               S01:00009D0C:  01 00 57 E3
F00:3549               ldmlefd sp!, {r4, r6, pc}     ; @ Return, restoring r4 and r6
               S01:00009D10:  50 80 BD D8
F00:3550       
F00:3551               ldr     r7, [r0, r1, asl #4]  ; @ r7 <- a[left], gets pivot element   	Z
               S01:00009D14:  01 72 90 E7
F00:3552       		
F00:3553               add     r2, r1, #1            ; @ l <- left + 1
               S01:00009D18:  01 20 81 E2
F00:3554               mov     r4, r6                ; @ r <- right
               S01:00009D1C:  06 40 A0 E1
F00:3555       		
F00:3556       		
F00:3557       qsort2_partition_loop:
F00:3558               ldr     r3, [r0, r2, asl #4]  ; @ r3 <- a[l]							Z
               S01:00009D20:  02 32 90 E7
F00:3559       
F00:3560               cmp     r3, r7                ; @ If a[l] <= pivot_element,
               S01:00009D24:  07 00 53 E1
F00:3561               addle   r2, r2, #1            ; @ ... increment l, and										SENS DU TRI
               S01:00009D28:  01 20 82 D2
F00:3562               ble     qsort2_partition_test        ; @ ... continue to next iteration.					SENS DU TRI
               S01:00009D2C:  12 00 00 DA
F00:3563       
F00:3564               sub     r4, r4, #1            ; @ Otherwise, decrement r,
               S01:00009D30:  01 40 44 E2
F00:3565               ldr     r5, [r0, r4, asl #4]  ; @ ... and swap a[l] and a[r].
               S01:00009D34:  04 52 90 E7
F00:3566               str     r5, [r0, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009D38:  02 52 80 E7
F00:3567               str     r3, [r0, r4, asl #4]
               S01:00009D3C:  04 32 80 E7
F00:3568       		
F00:3569       ; X
F00:3570       		sub		R12,R0,#8				; position en X
               S01:00009D40:  08 C0 40 E2
F00:3571       		ldr     r3, [r12, r2, asl #4]		; X1
               S01:00009D44:  02 32 9C E7
F00:3572       		ldr     r5, [r12, r4, asl #4]		; X2
               S01:00009D48:  04 52 9C E7
F00:3573       		str     r5, [r12, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009D4C:  02 52 8C E7
F00:3574       		str     r3, [r12, r4, asl #4]
               S01:00009D50:  04 32 8C E7
F00:3575       ; Y
F00:3576       		add		R12,R12,#4				; position en Y
               S01:00009D54:  04 C0 8C E2
F00:3577       		ldr     r3, [r12, r2, asl #4]		; Y1
               S01:00009D58:  02 32 9C E7
F00:3578       		ldr     r5, [r12, r4, asl #4]		; Y2
               S01:00009D5C:  04 52 9C E7
F00:3579       		str     r5, [r12, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009D60:  02 52 8C E7
F00:3580       		str     r3, [r12, r4, asl #4]
               S01:00009D64:  04 32 8C E7
F00:3581       ; n° sprite
F00:3582       		add		R12,R12,#8				; position en n° sprite
               S01:00009D68:  08 C0 8C E2
F00:3583       		ldr     r3, [r12, r2, asl #4]		; 1
               S01:00009D6C:  02 32 9C E7
F00:3584       		ldr     r5, [r12, r4, asl #4]		; 2
               S01:00009D70:  04 52 9C E7
F00:3585       		str     r5, [r12, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009D74:  02 52 8C E7
F00:3586       		str     r3, [r12, r4, asl #4]
               S01:00009D78:  04 32 8C E7
F00:3587       		
F00:3588       		
F00:3589       
F00:3590       qsort2_partition_test:
F00:3591               cmp     r2, r4                ; @ If l < r,
               S01:00009D7C:  04 00 52 E1
F00:3592               blt     qsort2_partition_loop        ; @ ... continue iterating.
               S01:00009D80:  E6 FF FF BA
F00:3593       
F00:3594       qsort2_partition_finish:
F00:3595               sub     r2, r2, #1            ; @ Decrement l
               S01:00009D84:  01 20 42 E2
F00:3596               ldr     r3, [r0, r2, asl #4]  ; @ Swap a[l] and pivot
               S01:00009D88:  02 32 90 E7
F00:3597               str     r3, [r0, r1, asl #4]
               S01:00009D8C:  01 32 80 E7
F00:3598               str     r7, [r0, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009D90:  02 72 80 E7
F00:3599       
F00:3600       ; X
F00:3601       		sub		R12,R0,#8				; position en X		
               S01:00009D94:  08 C0 40 E2
F00:3602       		ldr     r3, [r12, r2, asl #4]		; X1
               S01:00009D98:  02 32 9C E7
F00:3603       		ldr     r5, [r12, r1, asl #4]		; X2
               S01:00009D9C:  01 52 9C E7
F00:3604       		str     r5, [r12, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009DA0:  02 52 8C E7
F00:3605       		str     r3, [r12, r1, asl #4]
               S01:00009DA4:  01 32 8C E7
F00:3606       ; Y
F00:3607       		add		R12,R12,#4				; position en Y
               S01:00009DA8:  04 C0 8C E2
F00:3608       		ldr     r3, [r12, r2, asl #4]		; Y1
               S01:00009DAC:  02 32 9C E7
F00:3609       		ldr     r5, [r12, r1, asl #4]		; Y2
               S01:00009DB0:  01 52 9C E7
F00:3610       		str     r5, [r12, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009DB4:  02 52 8C E7
F00:3611       		str     r3, [r12, r1, asl #4]
               S01:00009DB8:  01 32 8C E7
F00:3612       ; n° sprite
F00:3613       		add		R12,R12,#8				; position en n° sprite
               S01:00009DBC:  08 C0 8C E2
F00:3614       		ldr     r3, [r12, r2, asl #4]		; 1
               S01:00009DC0:  02 32 9C E7
F00:3615       		ldr     r5, [r12, r1, asl #4]		; 2
               S01:00009DC4:  01 52 9C E7
F00:3616       		str     r5, [r12, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009DC8:  02 52 8C E7
F00:3617       		str     r3, [r12, r1, asl #4]		
               S01:00009DCC:  01 32 8C E7
F00:3618       		
F00:3619       		
F00:3620               bl      qsort2_qsort                ;@ Call self recursively on left part,
               S01:00009DD0:  CA FF FF EB
F00:3621                                             ;@  with args a (r0), left (r1), r (r2),
F00:3622                                             ;@  also preserves r4 and r6
F00:3623               mov     r1, r4
               S01:00009DD4:  04 10 A0 E1
F00:3624               b       qsort2_qsort_tailcall_entry  ; @ Tail-call self on right part,
               S01:00009DD8:  CA FF FF EA
F00:3625                                             ; @  with args a (r0), l (r1), right (r6)
F00:3626       
F00:3627

F00:3629       masque_decodage_X:			.long 0b11111111111111111110000000000000
               S01:00009DDC:  00 E0 FF FF

F20:0001       ; ============================================================================
F20:0002       ; Palette Utils
F20:0003       ; ============================================================================
F20:0004       
F20:0005       ; R3 = index
F20:0006       ; R4 = RGBx word   //   0BGR 0000
F20:0007       ; Uses R0,R1 
F20:0008       palette_set_colour:
F20:0009           adrl r1, palette_osword_block
               S01:00009DE0:  01 1C 8F E2 04 10 81 E2
F20:0010           strb r3, [r1, #0]       ; logical colour
               S01:00009DE8:  00 30 C1 E5
F20:0011       	
F20:0012           mov r0, #16
               S01:00009DEC:  10 00 A0 E3
F20:0013           strb r0, [r1, #1]       ; physical colour
               S01:00009DF0:  01 00 C1 E5
F20:0014       	
F20:0015           and r0, r4, #0x0f0000		; R 
               S01:00009DF4:  0F 08 04 E2
F20:0016       	mov r0, r0, lsr #16	
               S01:00009DF8:  20 08 A0 E1
F20:0017           strb r0, [r1, #2]       ; red
               S01:00009DFC:  02 00 C1 E5
F20:0018           
F20:0019       	mov r0, r4, lsr #2
               S01:00009E00:  24 01 A0 E1
F20:0020       	and r0,r0,#0x0f
               S01:00009E04:  0F 00 00 E2
F20:0021           strb r0, [r1, #3]       ; green
               S01:00009E08:  03 00 C1 E5
F20:0022           
F20:0023       	mov r0, r4, lsr #24
               S01:00009E0C:  24 0C A0 E1
F20:0024       	and r0,r0,#0x0f
               S01:00009E10:  0F 00 00 E2
F20:0025           strb r0, [r1, #4]       ; blue
               S01:00009E14:  04 00 C1 E5
F20:0026           
F20:0027       	mov r0, #12
               S01:00009E18:  0C 00 A0 E3
F20:0028           swi OS_Word
               S01:00009E1C:  07 00 00 EF
F20:0029       	
F20:0030           mov pc,lr
               S01:00009E20:  0E F0 A0 E1
F20:0031       
F20:0032       ; R2 = palette block ptr
F20:0033       palette_set_block:
F20:0034       	str lr, [sp, #-4]!			; push lr on stack
               S01:00009E24:  04 E0 2D E5
F20:0035           mov r3, #0
               S01:00009E28:  00 30 A0 E3
F20:0036           .1:
F20:0037           ldr r4, [r2], #4            ; rgbx
               S01:00009E2C:  04 40 92 E4
F20:0038           bl palette_set_colour
               S01:00009E30:  EA FF FF EB
F20:0039           add r3, r3, #1
               S01:00009E34:  01 30 83 E2
F20:0040           cmp r3, #16
               S01:00009E38:  10 00 53 E3
F20:0041           blt .1
               S01:00009E3C:  FA FF FF BA
F20:0042       	ldr pc, [sp], #4			; rts
               S01:00009E40:  04 F0 9D E4
F20:0043       
F20:0044       ; R2 = palette block ptr
F20:0045       palette_make_greyscale:
F20:0046       	str lr, [sp, #-4]!			; push lr on stack
               S01:00009E44:  04 E0 2D E5
F20:0047           adr r1, palette_interp_block
               S01:00009E48:  A8 10 8F E2
F20:0048       
F20:0049           mov r3, #16
               S01:00009E4C:  10 30 A0 E3
F20:0050           .1:
F20:0051           ldr r4, [r2], #4            ; rgbx
               S01:00009E50:  04 40 92 E4
F20:0052       
F20:0053           mov r5, r4, lsr #2          ; red * 0.25
               S01:00009E54:  24 51 A0 E1
F20:0054           and r5, r5, #0xf0
               S01:00009E58:  F0 50 05 E2
F20:0055           mov r6, r4, lsr #9          ; green * 0.5
               S01:00009E5C:  A4 64 A0 E1
F20:0056           and r6, r6, #0xf0
               S01:00009E60:  F0 60 06 E2
F20:0057           mov r7, r4, lsr #18         ; blue * 0.25
               S01:00009E64:  24 79 A0 E1
F20:0058           and r7, r7, #0xf0
               S01:00009E68:  F0 70 07 E2
F20:0059           
F20:0060           add r0, r5, r6
               S01:00009E6C:  06 00 85 E0
F20:0061           add r0, r0, r7
               S01:00009E70:  07 00 80 E0
F20:0062           orr r0, r0, r0, lsl #8
               S01:00009E74:  00 04 80 E1
F20:0063           orr r0, r0, r0, lsl #8
               S01:00009E78:  00 04 80 E1
F20:0064       
F20:0065           str r0, [r1], #4
               S01:00009E7C:  04 00 81 E4
F20:0066           
F20:0067           subs r3, r3, #1
               S01:00009E80:  01 30 53 E2
F20:0068           bne .1
               S01:00009E84:  F1 FF FF 1A
F20:0069       	ldr pc, [sp], #4			; rts
               S01:00009E88:  04 F0 9D E4
F20:0070       
F20:0071       ; R0 = [0-16] interpolation
F20:0072       ; R2 = palette block ptr
F20:0073       palette_make_fade_to_black:
F20:0074       	str lr, [sp, #-4]!			; push lr on stack
               S01:00009E8C:  04 E0 2D E5
F20:0075           adr r1, palette_interp_block
               S01:00009E90:  60 10 8F E2
F20:0076       
F20:0077           mov r3, #16
               S01:00009E94:  10 30 A0 E3
F20:0078           .1:
F20:0079           ldr r4, [r2], #4            ; rgbx
               S01:00009E98:  04 40 92 E4
F20:0080       
F20:0081           mov r5, r4, lsr #4          ; rgbx / 16
               S01:00009E9C:  24 52 A0 E1
F20:0082           mul r6, r5, r0              ; r0 * rgbx / 16
               S01:00009EA0:  95 00 06 E0
F20:0083       
F20:0084           str r6, [r1], #4
               S01:00009EA4:  04 60 81 E4
F20:0085           
F20:0086           subs r3, r3, #1
               S01:00009EA8:  01 30 53 E2
F20:0087           bne .1
               S01:00009EAC:  F9 FF FF 1A
F20:0088       	ldr pc, [sp], #4			; rts
               S01:00009EB0:  04 F0 9D E4
F20:0089       
F20:0090       ; R0 = [0-16] interpolation
F20:0091       ; R2 = palette block ptr
F20:0092       palette_make_fade_to_white:
F20:0093       	str lr, [sp, #-4]!			; push lr on stack
               S01:00009EB4:  04 E0 2D E5
F20:0094           adr r1, palette_interp_block
               S01:00009EB8:  38 10 8F E2
F20:0095       
F20:0096           add r1, r1, #4              ; ignore 0
               S01:00009EBC:  04 10 81 E2
F20:0097           add r2, r2, #4              ; ignore 0
               S01:00009EC0:  04 20 82 E2
F20:0098       
F20:0099           ldr r7, solid_white
               S01:00009EC4:  28 70 9F E5
F20:0100           mov r3, #15
               S01:00009EC8:  0F 30 A0 E3
F20:0101           .1:
F20:0102           ldr r4, [r2], #4            ; rgbx
               S01:00009ECC:  04 40 92 E4
F20:0103       
F20:0104           sub r5, r7, r4              ; white - rgbx
               S01:00009ED0:  04 50 47 E0
F20:0105           mov r5, r5, lsr #4          ; (white - rgbx) / 16
               S01:00009ED4:  25 52 A0 E1
F20:0106           mla r6, r5, r0, r4          ; rgbx + r0 * (white - rgbx) / 16
               S01:00009ED8:  95 40 26 E0
F20:0107       
F20:0108           str r6, [r1], #4
               S01:00009EDC:  04 60 81 E4
F20:0109           
F20:0110           subs r3, r3, #1
               S01:00009EE0:  01 30 53 E2
F20:0111           bne .1
               S01:00009EE4:  F8 FF FF 1A
F20:0112       	ldr pc, [sp], #4			; rts
               S01:00009EE8:  04 F0 9D E4
